[SN]TITLE[SN]
Barcelona v Real Madrid: Who would you pick in a combined best XI?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Cristiano Ronaldo? Lionel Messi? Neymar? Karim Benzema? Sergio Ramos? Gerard Pique? Sergio Busquets? Toni Kroos?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
If you had the squads of Barcelona and Real Madrid at your disposal, who would you choose?
And yes, we know Gareth Bale is out of Saturday's El Clasico (15:15 GMT kick-off), but we've given you the option of picking the Welshman too.
Pick yours - if you can - and share it with your friends.
Imagine you could pick from the combined squads of Barcelona and Real Madrid - tasty but testing. Who would you choose?
